ih.kg/1304865\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304865</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n對連儂牆既一啲諗法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304579\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304579</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n［置頂，極緊要，極長文］唔好再話連儂牆無用也也也，連儂牆甚至可能係呢一場運動既致勝關鍵！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1301800\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1301800</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n共產黨其實怕我地搞地區工作多過出金鐘<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304935\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304935</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"55bf46b5d0cb42ae370f9442917ad05fe7377708","tid":1310202,"uid":117276,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T16:58:14.000Z","msg":"去金鐘先<br />\n之後先睇重播<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a36071f0d9b9bcc5e7046951c394afacc282f206","tid":1310202,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T16:59:26.000Z","msg":"21號升級喎....."},{"pid":"b72b685c536d19c1a20cd681c8b83833f7aeaf5e","tid":1310202,"uid":87985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T17:00:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">去金鐘先，之前先睇返直播！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"32590361e89958f944218295482baf35dd2f58f3","tid":1310202,"uid":136393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T04:46:53.000Z","msg":"冇直播<br />\n之後會放返片出黎<br />\n金鐘急既去咗先"}]}